    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>(enough to cover the base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated veg</strong> (spread them out as much as possible) and cook for 4-5 min on each side until golden – this is your <strong>crispy veg</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use two pans!</p><p>Once crispy, transfer to a plate and set aside, reserve the pan</p>",
