    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is cooking, wash, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, de-seed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Stir the <strong>sliced spring onions</strong> and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) into the cooked rice – this is your<strong> chilli rice</strong></p>",
