    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium low heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>lemon sauce</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce is thick and sticky</p>",
